```json
  "clientKey": "userxxxxx-2782xx2-065e-x-7daa-xxxxx",
  "task": {
    "type": "BinanceClassification",
    "images": [
      ""
    ],
    "slice": [],
    "question": "binance_slide:Slide to complete the puzzle",
    "websiteURL": "accounts.binance.com"
  }
}
```
